Frontend:
- Remove the labels from home page and move the creation, editting and deleting of the labels to the label page.
- Move the importing of the labels to a right vertical menu that can be collapsed and expanded on the main page where are the transfers are listed.
- Auto update the transfers in the home "transfer page" if the transfers are uploaded and processed.
- Use the table styling from the transfers also for the bank accounts and labels
- Add an action column for bank accounts and labels
- Add an edit button for a bank account
- Also show if the bank account is internal yes or no (can be done with a sort of checkmark after the name)
- Add an edit page for a bank account (You are allowed to change the name)

Backend:
- If a label is created, auto assign it to already existing transfers, based on the rules of that label (linked bank account or regex)
- Not only link regexes based on the reference of the transfer, but also on the account name.
- If a bank account is updated, check if the automated linked labels are still valid and update them accordingly.
- If a label is updated, check if the automated linked bank accounts are still valid and update them accordingly.